   <talk_paragraph index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-accepting" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-accepting-a" mid="6" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Uh oh...she's in one of her moods...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Tiana${action:Talk}<BR>I am sick of these silly adventurers with their giant swords and empty heads!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-accepting-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-accepting-b" mid="8" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Well.. magic is just as important as strength.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Tiana$<BR>I heard that, you must be one of them who think brawn is better than magic, hm? </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-accepting-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-accepting-c" mid="10" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Tiana$<BR>I've seen those thugs with the huge swords or hammers or whatever scurrying all over town. Morons!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-accepting-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-accepting-d" mid="14" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>How to fight a real battle?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Tiana$<BR>Sometimes, carrying a large weapon will only hurt your shoulders and tire you out. No one knows how to fight a real battle anymore... It's so sad...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-accepting-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-accepting-e" mid="16" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Elegant battles...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Tiana$<BR>Yes. It's so ugly to swing swords until you get a dislocated shoulder. Battles are meant to be elegant.<FONT color=#a82424>(Tiana stretches her arm)</FONT> Elegant like this. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-accepting-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-accepting-f" mid="18" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Tiana$<BR>What's with that expression? You can fight more elegantly if you use magic but everyone's obsessed with power or stamina or… I just don't understand</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-accepting-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-accepting-g" mid="19" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I don't know…I'll think about it...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Tiana$<BR>Hmm... You have a cute face. I will specially teach you how to fight elegantly. Are you interested?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-accepting-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-accepting-h" mid="21" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Monster? Does that make me a monster?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Tiana$<BR>If you take my lesson, you will be able to get the title <FONT color=#a82424>Monster</FONT>… </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-accepting-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-accepting-i" mid="23" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Okay.. I'm interested!!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Tiana$<BR>...What? Why... No!<BR>The Monster title is for those who have shown their dominance over the demonic forces. It <FONT color=#a82424>enhances your intelligence</FONT> so you can use more powerful magic.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-accepting-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-accepting-acceptted" mid="25" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#086171>Accept Quest</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>$Grace Under Pressure I$</html>]]></talk_question>
