   <talk_paragraph index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-3-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-3-d" mid="48" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>How can you fight elegantly?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="47"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Tiana$<BR>I can see that you have some basics but… you still lack elegance to be worthy of the Monster title.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-3-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-3-e" mid="50" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>… I have no idea..</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="49"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Tiana$<BR>You know, something like… being soft and elegant like the swan's feathers and tasteful like the cheese cake… soft and sweet~</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-3-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-3-f" mid="45" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="44"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Tiana$<BR>Hmmph, I guess you're too immature to understand this high level beauty yet. But real grace will come out under danger. I should give you a more difficult task this time.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-3-f" image="QW_26.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-3-g" mid="52" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>…but did anyone manage to survive using only those "elegant moves"?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="51"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Tiana$<BR>There is an ancient evil spirit called <FONT color=#a82424>Shadow Dark</FONT> at <FONT color=#a82424>Sanctuary Core</FONT>. That fella can't stand people who lack elegance and slices them with his scythe.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-3-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-3-h" mid="54" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>You aren't really going to send me to fight that one… are you?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="53"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Tiana$<BR>If you do, you'll be the first! Haha!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-3-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n035_soceress_master_tiana-3-!next" mid="56" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I'll try.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="55"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Tiana$<BR>Of course, I am! Go and show that monster what true elegance is. Classy magic would kill that stupid monster in one blow, am I right?</html>]]></talk_question>
